  "title": "Beautician Consultant #81687",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Medical Aesthetic/ Skincare</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Beautician Consultant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Islandwide (City Hall, Dhoby Ghaut, Paya Lebar)</li><li>Working Hours: Monday to Friday 11am - 9pm, Saturday from 10am - 8pm and Sunday 10am - 7pm (Follow roster)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + Commission + Sales Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform facial, slimming, and hair removal treatments for customers based on company procedures.</li><li>Keep the treatment area clean and ready before and after each session.</li><li>Conduct consultations to understand customers’ goals, preferences, and physical condition.</li><li>Recommend beauty products and services that match each customer’s needs.</li><li>Follow up with customers after treatments to check results and satisfaction, and to encourage repeat visits.</li><li>Keep accurate records of customer details, preferences, and treatment progress.</li><li>Manage stock and ensure supplies are tracked and replenished when needed.</li><li>Attend internal training and workshops to maintain service standards.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least 3 years of hands-on experience performing facial or slimming treatments</li><li>Experience in hair removal treatments is a plus</li><li>Basic computer skills to manage customer bookings and records</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81687 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
